{"tid":921544,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"浸大調查：僅三成受訪者信任傳統新聞機構","createTime":"2018-11-29T15:46:09.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-29T22:57:42.000Z","uid":79563,"like":10,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"936646be15b668b5c3fa688c444a02784fbe5a54","tid":921544,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-29T15:46:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://fs.mingpao.com/ins/20181129/s00001/b75af2499b1104fbd58fbbfc601e55d2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F20181129%2Fs00001%2Fb75af2499b1104fbd58fbbfc601e55d2.jpg&h=933ca2a2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n香港浸會大學傳理學院發表《香港媒體數碼發展報告2018》，發現電視及電子版報紙是市民獲取新聞資訊的主要來源，但只得三成受訪者表示信任傳統新聞機構。<br />\n<br />\n研究歷時半年，團隊共20人，分別向1000名市民進行電話調查、255名媒體從業員填寫網上問卷及專訪13名媒體主管，涵蓋本港87間媒體。<br />\n<br />\n研究結果發現，在1000名受訪市民中，電視是受訪者（84.7%）獲取新聞資訊的主要來源、其次為電子版報紙（55.6%）、第三是透過社交媒體的分享（46.2%），當中受訪者最常使用的社交媒體平台是Facebook（38.4%）。學院新聞系中文新聞專修課程主任李文稱，與其他國家相比，本港市民使用社交媒體獲得新聞資訊的比例屬偏高，如法國只有36%、德國只得31%。<br />\n<br />\n不過，結果發現，只得30.8%受訪者信任傳統新聞機構，66.6%受訪者表示一般或不信任。至於網上媒體及社交媒體上分享的新聞資訊，分別只得17.9%及5.9%受訪者表示信任。李文稱，不少受訪者使用社交媒體獲取新聞資訊，卻不相信內容，兩者有矛盾。他說，不少歐美國家亦有同樣情況，此現象值得再探討。研究助理教授張引估計，市民日常接觸資訊眾多，但各媒體資訊內容並不一致，故會影響市民觀感。"},{"pid":"0207286ea99c0cf53da694c9ca965d7299c42801","tid":921544,"uid":38904,"like":18,"dislike":0,"score":18,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-29T15:46:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://media.giphy.com/media/26n6ziTEeDDbowBkQ/giphy.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmedia.giphy.com%2Fmedia%2F26n6ziTEeDDbowBkQ%2Fgiphy.gif&h=b8627516&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"af3807d34c4838d809622937f1880574557ccaa3","tid":921544,"uid":158270,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-29T17:05:45.000Z","msg":"好開始"},{"pid":"69a0afcfc40ab70414c7a64acecd55199e402e77","tid":921544,"uid":26506,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"af3807d34c4838d809622937f1880574557ccaa3","tid":921544,"uid":158270,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-29T17:05:45.000Z","msg":"好開始"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-11-29T17:11:11.000Z","msg":"&gt; 電視是受訪者（84.7%）獲取新聞資訊的主要來源 <br />\n你話睇Now同有線就係啫"},{"pid":"109a02e1d0fa3048f56fb429edb4a12cbbad5fcf","tid":921544,"uid":4783,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-29T17:12:30.000Z","msg":"fake news<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"523a4f057a3a479664f9200027f51af20756dd0f","tid":921544,"uid":158270,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"69a0afcfc40ab70414c7a64acecd55199e402e77","tid":921544,"uid":26506,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"af3807d34c4838d809622937f1880574557ccaa3","tid":921544,"uid":158270,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-29T17:05:45.000Z","msg":"好開始"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-11-29T17:11:11.000Z","msg":"&gt; 電視是受訪者（84.7%）獲取新聞資訊的主要來源 <br />\n你話睇Now同有線就係啫"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-29T17:35:36.000Z","msg":"自從香港傳媒團上完京之後，99台好似收歛咗"},{"pid":"c27f5c1d1565149c38af79cbef3f6c8bb3d58d9c","tid":921544,"uid":51701,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-29T21:19:48.000Z","msg":"cctvb<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"094fcfe608646f9558a39098e2c97e33bb39d0bd","tid":921544,"uid":52595,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-29T21:22:45.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"6578b6c07f1332bce7b5934f646472606c0ff153","tid":921544,"uid":63909,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"69a0afcfc40ab70414c7a64acecd55199e402e77","tid":921544,"uid":26506,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"af3807d34c4838d809622937f1880574557ccaa3","tid":921544,"uid":158270,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-29T17:05:45.000Z","msg":"好開始"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-11-29T17:11:11.000Z","msg":"&gt; 電視是受訪者（84.7%）獲取新聞資訊的主要來源 <br />\n你話睇Now同有線就係啫"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-29T22:43:51.000Z","msg":"其實now 新聞好閪架<img src=\"/assets/fa